  m_text: 'As soon as i entered the main house, the heavy wooden doors forcefully
    slammed shut behind me, sealing me inside. Fortunately, the first clue i had
    uncovered back in the town''s graveyard made my next objective clear. GO TO THE
    GRAVEYARD

'
